## â–¶ï¸ How to Run in Google Colab

1. Open the notebook  
   ```
   notebooks/pneumonia_detection.ipynb
   ```

2. Upload the dataset (or download from Kaggle using API)

3. Enable GPU  
   **Runtime â†’ Change runtime type â†’ GPU**

4. Install dependencies  
   ```
   !pip install tensorflow matplotlib sklearn
   ```

5. Run all cells to train and evaluate the model.

